nl.tue.fingerpaint.client.resources

Interface FingerpaintConstants

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.google.gwt.i18n.client.Constants, com.google.gwt.i18n.shared.Localizable, com.google.gwt.i18n.client.LocalizableResource

    public interface FingerpaintConstants
extends com.google.gwt.i18n.client.Constants
    The FingerpaintConstants are a set of localised constants. They can be used in the GUI for I18N for example.
    Author:
    Group Fingerpaint
